<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:13:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国查获350多个从中国进口枪支零部件的网站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-seizes-over-350-websites-used-import-gun-parts-china-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国当局周三表示，他们查获了超过 350 个销售枪支消音器和来自中国的零部件的网站，这些零部件用于将半自动手枪改装成全自动机枪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 20:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-seizes-over-350-websites-used-import-gun-parts-china-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国FDA向两家违反实验室规范的中国公司发出警告信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-fda-sends-warning-letters-two-chinese-firms-violating-lab-practices-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国食品和药物管理局周三向两家中国第三方检测公司发出警告信，理由是监管失误和动物护理违规行为，引发了人们对实验室生成数据的质量和完整性的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 18:36:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-fda-sends-warning-letters-two-chinese-firms-violating-lab-practices-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国贸易长官下周将在意大利举行贸易谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-trade-chief-set-talks-trade-italy-next-week-2024-09-11/</link><description>意大利政府消息人士周三表示，中国最高贸易官员将于下周抵达意大利进行会谈，北京方面正试图说服欧盟成员国拒绝欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的提议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 16:42:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-trade-chief-set-talks-trade-italy-next-week-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国吉利为欧洲工厂寻找选址</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-scouting-locations-europe-plant-2024-09-11/</link><description>中国汽车制造商吉利汽车集团的高管在法兰克福接受路透社采访时表示，该公司正在欧洲寻找工厂选址，但尚未完全致力于建立本地生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 15:47:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-scouting-locations-europe-plant-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国和菲律宾就有争议的萨宾娜浅滩举行“坦诚”会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-hold-frank-talks-disputed-sabina-shoal-2024-09-11/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国外交部副部长和菲律宾副外长就海洋相关问题，特别是有争议的萨比纳浅滩问题进行了“坦诚、深入”的交流。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 15:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-hold-frank-talks-disputed-sabina-shoal-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>普京称俄罗斯应考虑限制铀、钛和镍出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/putin-says-russia-should-consider-restricting-exports-uranium-titanium-nickel-2024-09-11/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周三表示，莫斯科应考虑限制铀、钛和镍的出口，以报复西方制裁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 14:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/putin-says-russia-should-consider-restricting-exports-uranium-titanium-nickel-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称如果面临威胁可能与中国“联合”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-could-combine-with-china-if-they-faced-threat-2024-09-11/</link><description>俄罗斯周三表示，其与中国的伙伴关系并非针对第三国，但如果面临美国的威胁，两国可以“结合潜力”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 14:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-could-combine-with-china-if-they-faced-threat-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国、意大利和西班牙均赢得戴维斯杯揭幕战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/united-states-win-davis-cup-opener-against-chile-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国队周三战胜了智利队，开始了戴维斯杯决赛小组赛阶段的比赛，尽管多名顶级单打选手缺席。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:52:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/united-states-win-davis-cup-opener-against-chile-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>印度将对从中国和越南进口的部分钢铁征收高达30%的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-impose-up-30-tariffs-some-steel-imports-china-vietnam-2024-09-11/</link><description>印度财政部的一项命令显示，印度将对从中国和越南进口的部分钢铁产品征收12%至30%的关税，以保护和促进当地工业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:36:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-impose-up-30-tariffs-some-steel-imports-china-vietnam-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>研究称，零排放卡车价格需要下降 50% 才能与柴油竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/emissions-free-truck-prices-need-drop-by-50-compete-with-diesel-study-says-2024-09-11/</link><description>咨询公司麦肯锡周三发布的一项研究称，无排放卡车的价格需要下降一半，才能成为柴油车型的负担得起的替代品，这是帮助实现欧盟气候目标的必要步骤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/emissions-free-truck-prices-need-drop-by-50-compete-with-diesel-study-says-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国将出台广泛措施改善保险业、防范风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issue-broad-measures-improve-insurance-sector-prevent-risks-2024-09-11/</link><description>一份声明称，中国国务院周三表示，将出台具体指导意见，加强保险业监管，防范保险业风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issue-broad-measures-improve-insurance-sector-prevent-risks-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>李克强与沙特王储在利雅得会面讨论合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/riyadh-chinas-premier-li-calls-accelerated-gulf-trade-talks-2024-09-11/</link><description>据沙特国家通讯社 SPA 报道，中国国务院总理李强和沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼周三在利雅得举行会议，讨论了能源、投资和贸易等多个领域的合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:28:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/riyadh-chinas-premier-li-calls-accelerated-gulf-trade-talks-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国孙俊浩否认中国关于足球比赛造假的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-koreas-son-jun-ho-denies-chinese-accusations-soccer-match-fixing-2024-09-11/</link><description>周三，韩国足球运动员孙俊浩含泪否认了中国当局对他在中国踢球时参与假球和贿赂的指控，并表示他是在胁迫下做出的虚假供述。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:38:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-koreas-son-jun-ho-denies-chinese-accusations-soccer-match-fixing-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：通胀观察的迅速变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-11/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：三星电子计划部分部门全球裁员高达30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsung-elec-plans-global-job-cuts-up-30-some-divisions-sources-say-2024-09-11/</link><description>三位直接了解此事的消息人士告诉路透社，全球最大的智能手机、电视和存储芯片制造商三星电子正在削减部分部门高达 30% 的海外员工。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 09:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsung-elec-plans-global-job-cuts-up-30-some-divisions-sources-say-2024-09-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>